00:22:39.960 --> 00:22:41.160
'cause I know somebody's gonna ask about this.

420
00:22:41.160 --> 00:22:44.100
How long do you treat for PMR and Giant Cell Arteritis?

421
00:22:44.100 --> 00:22:47.190
It depends. Treatment's gonna take a really, really,

422
00:22:47.190 --> 00:22:49.710
really long time, potentially up to a year

423
00:22:49.710 --> 00:22:52.440
and you're gonna have to really monitor patient symptoms,

424
00:22:52.440 --> 00:22:54.300
and also that sed rate.

425
00:22:54.300 --> 00:22:55.950
Some guidelines will say you come down

426
00:22:55.950 --> 00:22:59.730
by like one milligram, you know, just slowly.

427
00:22:59.730 --> 00:23:02.100
You know, I don't necessarily have to be

