00:23:03.120 --> 00:23:04.560
but you really, it takes a while.

430
00:23:04.560 --> 00:23:08.493
Okay. You do it too fast, you risk relapse. Okay.

431
00:23:09.420 --> 00:23:11.820
Alright. Get a call from the assisted living

