00:23:11.820 --> 00:23:15.153
patient had syncope getting up from the table after lunch.

433
00:23:16.110 --> 00:23:20.147
They're on hydrochlorothiazide, lisinopril for hypertension.

434
00:23:20.147 --> 00:23:25.095
When they finally get to her, there's the blood pressure.

435
00:23:25.095 --> 00:23:28.050
Oh, sorry. Otherwise you check back in the chart.

436
00:23:28.050 --> 00:23:29.610
Blood pressure's been consistently kind of

437
00:23:29.610 --> 00:23:32.460
around the 150 mark when you look in the review,

438
00:23:32.460 --> 00:23:34.053
the record, okay?

439
00:23:35.460 --> 00:23:39.540
Getting up after lunch, passing out, oh,

440
00:23:39.540 --> 00:23:41.280
we get called about this a lot.

441
00:23:41.280 --> 00:23:43.830
Remember I'm from Charleston, South Carolina. Okay?

442
00:23:45.300 --> 00:23:48.900
This is more common with high carb meals.

443
00:23:48.900 --> 00:23:52.710
All right. Our folks are having, you know,

444
00:23:52.710 --> 00:23:56.523
sweet tea biscuits, fried chicken.

445
00:23:57.660 --> 00:24:01.143
Okay? All the blood rushes to the gut.

446
00:24:03.420 --> 00:24:04.593
Gut's really happy.

