00:24:06.810 --> 00:24:09.303
and the brain's like, you forgot about me.

449
00:24:10.590 --> 00:24:15.590
All right. This would be a good board question too.

450
00:24:16.920 --> 00:24:18.780
Not an uncommon thing in your older adults.

451
00:24:18.780 --> 00:24:20.760
Ask them when they passed out, if they come in

